    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-border pt-8 mt-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text mb-4">Related</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li>→ <a href="/prop-firms/trader-career-path/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Trader Career Path full review</a></li>
        <li>→ <a href="/guides/trader-career-path-rules/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Every TCP rule explained</a></li>
        <li>→ <a href="/guides/earn2trade-consistency-rule/" class="text-primary hover:underline">The consistency rule that fails 91% of candidates</a></li>
