        <li>→ <a href="/review/ninjatrader/" class="text-primary hover:underline">NinjaTrader review</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <footer class="border-t border-border pt-6 mt-10 text-xs text-muted leading-relaxed">
      <p><strong class="text-text">Affiliate disclosure:</strong> TradingToolsHub earns a commission when you sign up for Earn2Trade through the links on this page. This does not change the price you pay.</p>
    </footer>

  </article>
</BaseLayout>
